0w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1777675450081_nn_cku_troops_germany_260501_S3_1920x1080-rqr13k.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">The Pentagon will withdraw roughly 5,000 U.S. troops from Germany, a move that comes amid President Trump’s growing clash with European allies over Iran and NATO tensions. NBC News’ Courtney Kube reports.</media:description><media:subTitle type="text/srt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1777675450081_nn_cku_troops_germany_260501.srt"></media:subTitle><media:subTitle type="text/vtt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1777675450081_nn_cku_troops_germany_260501.vtt"></media:subTitle></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1777675450081_nn_cku_troops_germany_260501_S3_1920x1080-rqr13k.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 22:44:16 GMT</pubDate><title>Trump administration to pull 5,000 troops from Germany</title><updateDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 23:15:42 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Steve Kopack</dc:creator><dc:contributor>Ryan Beckler</dc:contributor><dc:contributor>Ryan Nobles</dc:contributor><dc:contributor>Monica Alba</dc:contributor><dateTimeWritten>Fri, 01 May 2026 14:22:39 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>The national average gas price rose to $4.39 per gallon, in its biggest one-day jump since a ceasefire with Iran was announced on April 7.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/business/energy/gas-prices-iran-war-oil-ceasefire-rcna343053</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/business/energy/gas-prices-iran-war-oil-ceasefire-rcna343053</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260501-gas-pumps-gk-577e64.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Patrick T. Fallon</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Image: Vehicles sit parked at fuel pumps as regular gasoline prices above $6 per gallon and diesel prices above $7 per gallon are displayed outside a Mobil gas station </media:text><media:description type="plain">Vehicles sit parked at fuel pumps as regular gasoline prices above $6 per gallon and diesel prices above $7 per gallon are displayed outside a Mobil gas station in Redondo Beach, California on April 30, 2026. Energy costs have surged since the near-total closure of the Strait of Hormuz, through which about a fifth of the world&#39;s oil and gas usually passes, following the outbreak of the US-Israeli war against Iran.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260501-gas-pumps-gk-577e64.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 14:22:39 GMT</pubDate><title>Gas prices hit $4.39 per gallon in biggest one-day jump since Iran ceasefire announced</title><updateDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 22:14:36 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Fri, 01 May 2026 21:58:44 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Spirit Airlines could shut down as soon as Saturday, May 2, without a last-minute intervention, a source told NBC News. As of Friday afternoon, discussions about a rescue were ongoing, with Republican lawmakers opposing a proposed bailout of the budget carrier. </description><expires>2056-05-01T21:57:57.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">now_hallie_spirit_airlines_shutdown_260501</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/video/spirit-s-possible-shutdown-looms-after-bailout-plans-opposed-by-republicans-262559301942</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/now_hallie_spirit_airlines_shutdown_260501/1/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>Spirit&#39;s possible shutdown looms after bailout plans opposed by Republicans 