e Senate candidate</title><updateDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 11:00:41 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Alexander Smith</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Fri, 01 May 2026 22:22:34 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>LONDON — Britain in 2026 is a place where Jack Hur doesn’t feel safe wearing his Star of David pendant.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/world/united-kingdom/anger-despair-jewish-britons-spate-attacks-rcna342853</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/world/united-kingdom/anger-despair-jewish-britons-spate-attacks-rcna342853</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260501-london-stabbing-attack-mn-1230-dd17b6.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1200" width="1800"><media:credit>Lucy North</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Demonstrators rally in Whitehall, London, on April 30, 2026, following a stabbing attack. </media:text><media:description type="plain">Demonstrators rally in Whitehall, London, on April 30, 2026, following a stabbing attack. </media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260501-golders-green-jack-hur-mn-1240-f4e96d.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1622" width="1800"><media:credit>Alexander Smith</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Jack Hur in Golders Green.</media:text><media:description type="plain">Jack Hur in Golders Green.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260501-golders-green-Alvin-Ormonde-Ezra-Kahn-mn-1300-4fb8fd.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1200" width="1800"><media:credit>Alexander Smith</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Alvin Ormonde, left, and Ezra Kahn in Golders Green.</media:text><media:description type="plain">Alvin Ormonde, left, and Ezra Kahn in Golders Green.</media:description></medi